<p><strong>《变形金刚》</strong></p>
<p><strong>1986</strong></p>
<p><strong>Takara</strong></p>
<p></p>
<p><img src="//5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20180601/fd2b1f1cb1c04c38a29d3bf51615e62c.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
