<p><strong>1987</strong></p>
<p><strong>万代</strong></p>
<p><img src="//5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20180601/9b9ada35ebbe4542b5903b06fe93a6b1.jpg" max-width="600" /></p>
